▶️ EXECUTE

Introduction

The principe is to [INSTALL] ounce your project, then you can optionaly check the [DISTRIBUTE] ant then [RUN] it By default there is always a mode set, but if you don’t know which one to use then you can manually remove it from the snippet which will lead to a read in all modes for benchmarking

Sidebar

This is a listbox to select a project to be loaded from the existing ones.
